OL,3,CChoosing a new pope: How the Vatican
OL,4,Cturns its smoke signals black or white
OL,6,FTo create the white smoke, a mixture
OL,7,Fof potassium chloride, lactose, and
OL,8,Famber conifer resin is added to make
OL,9,Fit more visible.
OL,11,FShortly after a new pope is elected,
OL,12,Fhe steps onto the Vatican balcony,
OL,13,Fframed by red curtains, where he will
OL,14,Fdeliver his first apostolic blessing,
OL,15,Fknown as the "Urbi et Orbi" ("To the
OL,16,FCity and to the World"). This marks
OL,17,Fthe end of the conclave process.
